        "content": [
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "Val has been manually updating these every time we pay our referral fees."
              },
              {
                "type": "hardBreak"
              },
              {
                "type": "hardBreak"
              },
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "GL Account = 5100 · PARTICIPATION FEES EXPENSE:5115 · Participation Fees - WC"
              },
              {
                "type": "hardBreak"
              },
              {
                "type": "mediaInline",
                "attrs": {
                  "id": "9f7c0630-b949-4df6-af77-b2951706ebb2",
                  "collection": "",
                  "type": "file"
                }
              },
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": " "
              },
              {
                "type": "hardBreak"
              },
              {
                "type": "hardBreak"
              },
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "it runs off the Pay Participation Fee tab/flow"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "https://shulman-hill.lightning.force.com/lightning/n/Pay_Participation_Fees",
                "marks": [
                  {
                    "type": "link",
                    "attrs": {
                      "href": "https://shulman-hill.lightning.force.com/lightning/n/Pay_Participation_Fees"
                    }
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "specifically when we pay \"External Law Firms\" "
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": " "
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "the In-House Attorney is completely separate automation that is fine."
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": " "
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": "but when it creates fees for external firms, it's seting the line item tot eh old WC account. really the automation should set the line item based on the type of case/resolution. would need to flesh out the logic for it. There are fees for PI, SSD, WC, CR, and Referrals. Right now ti just all goes to the GL for WC....and the wrong/outdated one"
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "paragraph",
            "content": [
              {
                "type": "text",
                "text": " "
              }
            ]
          }
        ]
